{"tid":1321890,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"【置頂】721前線需知","createTime":"2019-07-15T19:39:55.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-16T19:39:27.000Z","uid":270250,"like":2,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"65e07d35897781ecb43ade42047947a6f541e001","tid":1321890,"uid":270250,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-15T19:39:55.000Z","msg":"【長文】<br />\n721要重裝<span style=\"color: red;\">FULL GEAR</span>就係人都知，仲有其他要點<br />\n<br />\n本人一直強調要升級，要升級抗爭向政府反抗，喺呢一刻我覺得要諗諗<br />\n<br />\n我啊哥係警察，係狗。佢應承過我唔會違背良心。佢係一個警司，我連自己都唔能夠說服自己佢冇份planning所以612之後就冇再見佢搵佢。去到今日佢不斷打俾我，有一次我聽左佢電話，佢講低左一段說話俾我聽。「如果喺示威者入面有一個人，乜人都唔關事，有一個人喺示威者度沖左出黎殺左差佬，你估會點呀」<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">狗</span></span>令各位手足好L嬲，令大家受傷，係要還手。但係請大家<span style=\"color: red;\">諗清楚</span>係咪要人地死先得<br />\n<br />\n如果有<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">狗</span></span> <span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">死</span></span>或者係比我地<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">死先</span></span>的話，政府可以戒嚴嫁。戒嚴就嚴重過沙田嗰一晚，戒嚴係可以全區封鎖大搜捕，而各位手足點樣嗌要搭地鐵點打鑊勁都好，都開唔到路走。而且佢地有絕對嘅理由將佢地嘅暴力升級，姐係有可能去到真槍。而呢一切係<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><del>合法</del></span><br />\n<br />\n除左<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">狗</span></span>嘅反應，仲有和理非，甚至游離派都會唔再支持我地。失民意會少左好多人買物資俾我地，少左義士幫手車物資。失民意個問題係會少左好多人喺後面backup我地，甚至我地可能會變成過街老鼠。<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">求下各位手足唔好俾佢地死</span>"},{"pid":"22d06f2351057733ddd3f5088b58f99167f5540b","tid":1321890,"uid":172754,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-15T19:40:10.000Z","msg":"(陰謀論) 送前線入浩園並唔係真正目的...<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1321857\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1321857</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"f32e088e2c62a4317335572868904ef935968829","tid":1321890,"uid":270250,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-15T19:40:36.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/rsB4CH9.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FrsB4CH9.jpg&h=972f9761&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"bbed8cda97a17b706fe2b295178e375d2d93cde9","tid":1321890,"uid":112748,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-16T19:39:27.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://youtu.be/h_pIvvIs4QE\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2Fh_pIvvIs4QE&d=VPbJsUOTS2%2BU35Cb01K8cFgnvSLZGSqUYyTYHJNLWIM%3D&h=cf4c4683\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/h_pIvvIs4QE</a>"}]}